OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,FThe UK Government has announced it is
OL,8,Fgiving an extra #3.45m to the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment to look at improvements to
OL,10,Fthe A75 in Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Secretary says it means
OL,13,Fthe UK Government is providing the
OL,14,F"full" funding for the feasibility
OL,15,Fstudy to consider bypassing two
OL,16,Fvillages on the road.
OL,18,FThe A75, which is a primary trunk road
OL,19,Fin Scotland, connects Stranraer and
OL,20,Fferry ports at Cairnryan to the M6 and
OL,21,FA74(M) at Gretna.
