OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,FIt serves as a crucial route for
OL,8,Ftraffic heading between Northern
OL,9,FIreland, England, and the rest of
OL,10,FScotland, particularly for those using
OL,11,Fthe ferries to Northern Ireland. It is
OL,12,Flargely single-carriageway, which can
OL,13,Flead to congestion, and longstanding
OL,14,Fsafety concerns.
OL,16,FIn 2023, the then Conservative
OL,17,Fgovernment at Westminster announced it
OL,18,Fwould provide #8m for the research
OL,19,Finto upgrading the A75.
