OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,FAfter Labour won the general election,
OL,8,Fthey announced at the Budget in
OL,9,FOctober 2024 they would provide up to
OL,10,F#5m towards the study. They say
OL,11,Ftoday's funding comes "on top" of that.
OL,13,FJohn Cooper, the Conservative MP for
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway, told ITV
OL,15,FBorder: It's telling that the money is
OL,16,Fa confirmation of funding earmarked by
OL,17,Fthe previous administration."
