OL,7,FToday's announcement is part of #66m
OL,8,Fannounced by the Chancellor for
OL,9,FScottish transport improvements.
OL,11,FThe UK Government describes the A75 as
OL,12,Fa "key road... vital to UK
OL,13,Fconnectivity and growing the economy."
