OL,7,FOn the topic, Scottish Secretary Ian
OL,8,FMurray said: "the A75 is strategically
OL,9,Fimportant just not within but beyond
OL,10,FScotland. Its upgrading is long
OL,11,Foverdue. I am pleased that the UK
OL,12,FGovernment has stepped up to fund the
OL,13,Fdelivery of the A75 feasibility study
OL,14,Fin full.
OL,16,F"This investment is yet another
OL,17,Fexample of how the UK Government is
OL,18,Fbuilding the foundations for a
OL,19,Fstronger, more prosperous future that
OL,20,Fbenefits communities right across
OL,21,FScotland."
