OL,7,FTransport Scotland says: "The
OL,8,Fstrategic importance of both the A75
OL,9,Fand A77 to Scotland's economy is
OL,10,Frecognised by this Government. We
OL,11,Fvalue the critical link they provide
OL,12,Fto the wider markets in the rest of
OL,13,Fthe UK and Europe by connecting the
OL,14,Fports at Cairnryan to the wider trunk
OL,15,Froad network.
