OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"Ministers have chaired the Convention
OL,8,Fof South of Scotland discussion on
OL,9,Ftransport, met the Leaders of Dumfries
OL,10,Fand Galloway and South Ayrshire
OL,11,FCouncils, had a roundtable discussion
OL,12,Fwith campaigners calling for road
OL,13,Fimprovements to the A75 and A77 in
OL,14,FGirvan, and also extended an offer to
OL,15,Fform a "South West Scotland Roads `
OL,16,FFocus Group". The purpose of this
OL,17,Fgroup is to improve the flow of
OL,18,Finformation with the campaign groups
OL,19,Fand wider stakeholders, and look at
OL,20,Flonger term strategic investment for
OL,21,Fboth the A75 and A77.
