OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"In terms of the A75 we have completed
OL,8,Fsix major roads improvement projects
OL,9,Fwith a total value of over #50
OL,10,Fmillion. While the UK Autumn Budget
OL,11,Fmarked a step in the right direction,
OL,12,Fit does not make up for fourteen years
OL,13,Fof underinvestment ` austerity cannot
OL,14,Fbe undone in one year. We are still
OL,15,Ffacing significant pressures on our
OL,16,Fcapital budget, which is significantly
OL,17,Faffecting our ability to maintain
OL,18,Finvestment on all of Scotland's
OL,19,Ftransport infrastructure.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
