OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"Additionally, we have wasted no time
OL,8,Fin progressing the design and
OL,9,Fassessment work to consider options
OL,10,Ffor realigning the A75 trunk road at
OL,11,Fthe villages of Springholm and
OL,12,FCrocketford."
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway MP, John Cooper,
OL,15,Fsaid: "While I am delighted the UK
OL,16,FGovernment is taking the view that the
OL,17,FA75 is of national importance, it's
OL,18,Ftelling that the money is a
OL,19,Fconfirmation of funding earmarked by
OL,20,Fthe previous administration.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
