OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"The road is critical to Dumfries &
OL,8,FGalloway as well as being the key link
OL,9,Ffor Northern Ireland to the rest of
OL,10,Fthe UK. The Scottish Government need
OL,11,Fto step up with some serious safety
OL,12,Fimprovements and stop pointing to
OL,13,Fbasic maintenance as though these were
OL,14,Fbig investments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/18
