OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"It's telling that outgoing Transport
OL,8,FSecretary Fiona Hyslop is still
OL,9,Frunning scared, refusing to meet me to
OL,10,Fdiscuss safety. There have been a slew
OL,11,Fof accidents in the A75 this summer
OL,12,Fand both Transport Scotland and Police
OL,13,FScotland are not proactive in putting
OL,14,Fout the statistics.
OL,16,F"The people of Dumfries & Galloway
OL,17,Fhave two governments, one in Holyrood
OL,18,Fand one in Westminster. Neither is
OL,19,Fseriously gripping the problems on the
OL,20,FA75, which is swamped by the size and
OL,21,Fsheer number of modern artic lorries."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/18
