OL,7,FFinlay Carson, Conservative MSP for
OL,8,FGalloway and West Dumfries, said:
OL,9,F"While any investment in Scotland's
OL,10,Ftransport infrastructure is welcome,
OL,11,Ftoday's announcement is deeply
OL,12,Fdisappointing for the people of
OL,13,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/18
