OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"The #66 million figure may sound
OL,8,Fimpressive, but in reality, in terms
OL,9,Fof the A75, it merely reinstates
OL,10,Ffunding previously committed by the UK
OL,11,FConservative Government. There is no
OL,12,Fnew money for the long-overdue upgrade
OL,13,Fof the A75 ` a route that is vital not
OL,14,Fjust for our region, but for the
OL,15,Fentire UK's connectivity with Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/18
