OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"Once again, we see a feasibility
OL,8,Fstudy offered in place of firm action.
OL,9,FThere is nothing for the A77!
OL,10,FCommunities across the South West have
OL,11,Fwaited far too long for meaningful
OL,12,Fprogress on this key strategic route.
OL,13,FThe time for studies is over ` we need
OL,14,Fa clear timetable and full funding for
OL,15,Fdelivery.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/18
