OL,3,COver #3m of funding could make A75
OL,4,Csafer after '14 years of
OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,F"Equally concerning is the continued
OL,8,Fsilence from the SNP-led Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment. Despite repeated calls
OL,10,Ffrom local residents, businesses, and
OL,11,Felected representatives, there remains
OL,12,Fno commitment from Holyrood to
OL,13,Fprioritise or fund the A75 upgrade.
OL,14,FThis lack of urgency is unacceptable
OL,15,Fand leaves our region at a
OL,16,Fdisadvantage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/18
