OL,5,Cunderinvestment'
OL,7,FI will continue to press both
OL,8,Fgovernments to stop passing the buck
OL,9,Fand start delivering the
OL,10,Finfrastructure improvements our
OL,11,Fcommunities deserve."
OL,13,FThis comes weeks after campaigners in
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway expressed
OL,15,Ffrustration that no money was
OL,16,Fannounced for the A75 in the UK
OL,17,FGovernment's spending review.
